<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting MemNote!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #2b2b2b;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h2 {
            color: #00bfff;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #e0e0e0; /* Brighter text for readability */
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .message-box {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #00bfff;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #f0f0f0; /* Bright text for the message box */
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaaaaa; /* Slightly brighter for readability */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Thank You for Contacting MemNote!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for contacting us! Your message has been received. For future reference, your message ID is: <strong style="color: #00bfff;">{{id}}</strong>.</p>
            <p><strong>Your Message:</strong></p>
            <div class="message-box">
                <p>{{message}}</p>
            </div>
            <p>If you need anything else in the meantime, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best Regards,<br>The MemNote Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
